      "description": "## Core\n\nFoundational API endpoints covering system health, coin data, sentiment analysis, backtesting, trending signals, and social scraping.\n\n### Endpoints\n\n| Method | Path | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| GET | `/api/health` | System health check — returns status of all dependent services |\n| GET | `/api/coins` | List all tracked coins with market data and sentiment scores |\n| GET | `/api/coins/:symbol` | Get detailed coin data with historical price and sentiment history |\n| POST | `/api/refresh-sentiment` | Trigger an async sentiment refresh job for all tracked coins |\n| GET | `/api/sentiment/:symbol` | Get the current sentiment breakdown for a specific coin |\n| POST | `/api/sentiment/analyze` | Analyze the sentiment of arbitrary text against a coin symbol |\n| POST | `/api/agents/configure` | Configure a MARL agent's trading parameters |\n| POST | `/api/backtest/run` | Submit a backtest job for a given strategy and date range |\n| GET | `/api/backtest/results/:testId` | Retrieve results for a completed backtest job |\n| GET | `/api/rankings/top-coins` | Get top-ranked coins by sentiment score for a given timeframe |\n| GET | `/api/info/modes` | List available trading modes supported by the system |\n| GET | `/api/scrape/social` | Scrape social media data for a specific coin symbol |\n| POST | `/api/scrape/batch` | Submit a batch scrape job for multiple symbols and platforms |\n| GET | `/api/trending` | Get currently trending coins based on volume and mention spikes |\n| POST | `/api/trending/ingest` | Ingest a trending data point from an external source |\n\n### Notes\n- `/api/health` does not require authentication and is safe to call frequently for uptime monitoring.\n- Backtest jobs are asynchronous — poll `/api/backtest/results/:testId` until `status` is `\"completed\"`.\n- Sentiment refresh and batch scrape jobs return a `jobId` for status tracking.",
